long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1273466 Screenshot of some desktop icons showing Chromium much lager than the others.
The size of the Chromium icon on the MATE desktop is noticably larger than the other icons. I am attaching a screenshot showing the differences.
Would it be possible to include smaller sized icons with Chromium, so the icon size can be consistent with the others? The package only includes one icon for the desktop, 256x256.
Thank you.
